description:
Fountainview Academy Orchestra and Singers perform their unforgettable rendition of the heart-touching hymn, The Love of God. The third stanza of hymn was written in the 11th century by a Jewish poet. The rest was composed in the early 20th century by American pastor Frederick Lehman.

Watch the Full Concert at:
https://adtv.watch/single-episode/i-sing-the-mighty-power-of-god
